Uses of Interface
eu.etaxonomy.cdm.model.common.IParsable

Packages that use IParsable
eu.etaxonomy.cdm.model.name Provides classes for nomenclature and typification. 
eu.etaxonomy.cdm.model.reference Provides classes for nomenclatural and bibliographical references either as a complex structure of specific subclasses according to the different kind of possible references used (see StrictReferenceBase class and subclasses) or as a flat structure (see BibTexReference class).
